<p>A <b>bitboard</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Data_structure" title="Data structure">data structure</a> commonly used in <a href="/wiki/Game_AI" title="Game AI" class="mw-redirect">computer systems that play</a> <a href="/wiki/Board_game" title="Board game">board games</a>.</p>
