<li><a href="http://www.onjava.com/pub/a/onjava/2005/02/02/bitsets.html" class="external text" title="http://www.onjava.com/pub/a/onjava/2005/02/02/bitsets.html" rel="nofollow">Pepicelli, Glen. <i>Bitfields, Bitboards, and Beyond</i></a> -(Example of bitboards in the Java Language and a discussion of why this optimization works with the Java Virtual Machine (www.OnJava.com publisher: O'Reilly 2005))</li>
</ul>
