<h5><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bitboard&amp;action=edit&amp;section=25" title="Edit section: Open source">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Open source</span></h5>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.frayn.net/beowulf/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.frayn.net/beowulf/index.html" rel="nofollow">Beowulf</a> Unix, Linux, Windows. Rotated bitboards.</li>
